::Cledar/Rixer/Forrior/Blyer::

Cledar and his group reach the CR chambers, finding that none of them 
were too damaged. He recieves the message from IR.

"You heard her. Lets go outside." He walks outside, his group 
following him. Spotting another group of Maximals (Alloran's), they 
walk toward them.
